#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><H3>
#: _includes/discussion.html:4
msgid "Quarkus's Collaborative Community Forum"
msgstr "Quarkus的合作社区论坛"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/discussion.html:5
msgid "The core foundation of every good open source project is open discussion and collaboration. Quarkus is committed to this belief. We've enabled GitHub Discussions so the community can have open communication. This gives a focal point for the community to ask and answer questions regarding the project. This means all of that great knowledge can be shared and is discoverable. Additionally, other conversations about the Quarkus Community can be had there as well. Come collaborate with us."
msgstr "每个好的开源项目的核心基础是公开讨论和合作。Quarkus致力于这一信念。我们已经启用了GitHub讨论，以便社区能够进行公开交流。这为社区提供了一个焦点，以提出和回答关于项目的问题。这意味着所有这些伟大的知识都可以被分享和发现。此外，关于Quarkus社区的其他对话也可以在这里进行。来与我们合作吧。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#. mt: deepl
#: _includes/discussion.html:6
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions\">Go to the Quarkus GitHub Discussions<i class=\"fas fa-external-link-alt\"></i></a>"
msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-right\"></i><a href=\"https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions\">前往 Quarkus GitHub 讨论区<i class=\"fas fa-external-link-alt\"></i></a>"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><h3>
#. mt: deepl
#: _includes/discussion.html:9
#, fuzzy
msgid "Community Call"
msgstr "社区电话会议"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#. mt: deepl
#: _includes/discussion.html:10
#, fuzzy
msgid "We host a biweekly Quarkus Community Call at 2PM (Paris time) to discuss technical topics and project updates. To attend, <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=Europe%2FParis\" target=\"blank\">view the calendar</a> or <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com/public/basic.ics\">subscribe (iCal)</a> to the calendar so you don't miss one. The calls are posted to Youtube you can view the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsM3ZE5tGAVZ_rG48SFUFpEyTYGai0YLw\" target=\"blank\">Community Call Playlist</a> to access all of the calls."
msgstr "我们每两周一次在巴黎时间下午2点举办Quarkus社区电话会议，讨论技术话题和项目进展。如需参加，<a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=Europe%2FParis\" target=\"blank\">请查看日历</a>或<a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/935090aaae38be35eda437d018782b7827f3770f7a0344013677acd861570b20%40group.calendar.google.com/public/basic.ics\">订阅（iCal）</a>该日历，以免错过任何一场会议。会议视频会发布在YouTube上，您可以查看<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsM3ZE5tGAVZ_rG48SFUFpEyTYGai0YLw\" target=\"blank\">“社区电话会议播放列表”</a>以观看所有会议视频。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><H3>
#: _includes/discussion.html:13
msgid "Quarkus Chat Options"
msgstr "Quarkus聊天选项"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#. mt: deepl
#: _includes/discussion.html:14
#, fuzzy
msgid "For usage questions, ask on <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/quarkus\">Stack Overflow with the <code>quarkus</code> tag</a>."
msgstr "如有使用方面的问题，请在<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/quarkus\">Stack Overflow 上使用<code>quarkus</code>标签</a>提问。"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
#: _includes/discussion.html:15
msgid "For questions related to the development of Quarkus:"
msgstr "对于与Quarkus自身开发相关的问题："

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><ul><li>
#. mt: deepl
#: _includes/discussion.html:17
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use the <a href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/forum/quarkus-dev\" target=\"_blank\">quarkus-dev Google Groups</a>"
msgstr "使用<a href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/forum/quarkus-dev\" target=\"_blank\">quarkus-dev Google 群组</a>"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><ul><li>
#: _includes/discussion.html:18
msgid "Chat using <a href=\"https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/187038-dev\" target=\"_blank\">Zulip</a> (<code>#dev</code> stream)"
msgstr "或在 <a href=\"https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/187038-dev\" target=\"_blank\">Zulip</a> (<code>#dev</code> stream) 聊天室发问。"
